downloadTitle: Installation Guide: Integration Solution White Paper for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012 Projects and Microsoft Dynamics CRM 2011
downloadDescription:
​This white paper explains the Integration Solution for Microsoft Dynamics AX 
2012 projects and Microsoft Dynamics CRM 2011, which enables you to integrate 
and synchronize your project quotation and project information.
detailsSection:
The Integration Solution for Microsoft Dynamics AX projects and Microsoft 
Dynamics CRM is built on the Microsoft Dynamics Connector. This white paper is a 
6-step installation guide for scenarios that involve synchronizing project 
quotations and project information between Microsoft Dynamics AX and Microsoft 
Dynamics CRM. Click the link to view or download the document.
